title: Nationwide AT&T Outage Affects Baltimore First Responders
text:
BALTIMORE (WJZ)– A nationwide AT&T issue has affected calls to 911 in the Baltimore area, according to Baltimore Police and Fire Departments.
If you have AT&T has a service provider, you’re asked to call 311 for emergencies.
